Originally ripped by Terminal Escape, posted on December 18, 2023 Description from Terminal Escape:
 A master clinic in thunderous noisecore crust from SORE THROAT. A whopping 92 tracks (the tape includes the Death To Capitalist Hardcore EP, because tapes rule of course) ranging from damaged light speed crust to chaotic sub-5 second blasts that challenge the concept of music itself. Sometimes you need a sonic reset, you know....? And still after all these years, I can listen to "War Is Horrendous" and "A Bow To Capital" on repeat - the rest of the tape is just a cherry on top of perfection. UNHINDERED BY TALENT
